@required {teamId: str # ID of the team the category belongs to, categoryId: str # Category to be updated}
@returns(200) Returns the updated category subscriptions
@errors {400: If the input is not valid, 403: If you have no permission to access this resource, 500: If any server side errors occur, 404: If the resource was not found}

